I"#<h4 id="grand-salon-interactive-wall">Grand Salon Interactive Wall</h4>

<p>The wall uses video tracking technology (Kinect) to view the bodies of event attendees who are standing or moving within a designated area. The software system connected to this array of sensors will use this 3D data to control an abstract visualization that appears on the video wall.</p>

<p>This visualization comprises of 2 ‘modes - Fluid and Particle’ each with a related but distinct appearance and behavior.</p>

